data.description: Back on the market, no fault of the seller’s, buyer’s financing fell through.  This beautiful  4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home is move in ready. With a bright & open kitchen which includes a  large granite island and new stainless steel appliances!  Walk right out and enjoy the extensive fenced in landscaped backyard which includes a deck and patio!  Main level includes a formal dining room, living room, den/office with built in shelves, powder room, and lovely two story family room.  Upper level  includes the spacious owner’s suite with built in walk in custom made closet, en suite owner’s bath with separate soaking tub and shower, 3 more very good sized bedrooms, and full bath.   The wide open basement is perfect for entertaining with  a wet bar, large storage area with built in shelving,  and another full bathroom! This property is located within a mile from the Dumfries commuter lot, 1.5 miles from I-95, and 3 miles from Quantico.  All of this and so much more!
